title: Sketches In The Key Of Life - Rob Tunbridge
description:
Rob Tunbridge is an unsigned singer/songwriter based in Chelmsford, Essex England.

You can find out more on myspace just search for Rob Tunbridge

This ZIP file contains the full album + Original Artwork in PDF Format


Tracks are MP3@192K and have been tested in i-tunes, windows media player, VLC Player


Tracks are:


 1. Out Of The Blue
 2. Stories For Boys
 3. The Affair Of Nina B
 4. Can You Take The Pressure?
 5. Here With Me (Sayuri's Song)
 6. Welcome To The 21st Century - (you can see the video on you tube)
 7. Me & You
 8. Do You Know What It's Like?
 9. Head Down, Boogie!
10. It's A Game (called life)
11. Into The Mirror
12. Friday 13
13. Photos In Babylon


Hope you like them!
